Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.26,1:44:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all you have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.28,1:44:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.72,1:44:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to see it in a greater light
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.80,1:44:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to reveal consciously
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.88,1:44:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to my conscious mind
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.04,1:44:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is there any significance in that
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.82,1:44:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it will
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.04,1:44:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,be dependable within a group
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.84,1:44:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,setting
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.92,1:44:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as I meditate alone
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.30,1:44:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this doesn't arise
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.20,1:44:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mhm
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.48,1:44:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so that's the being
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.98,1:44:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,part of a group
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.34,1:44:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and with others somehow
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.38,1:44:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.14,1:44:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that gives you sort of hints
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.62,1:44:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.92,1:44:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.44,1:44:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you really need a revelation
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.62,1:44:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to become aware of it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.97,1:44:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.47,1:44:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.07,1:44:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.25,1:44:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.61,1:44:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,help
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.09,1:44:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you sweetheart
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.87,1:44:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you dog
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.33,1:44:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes forth of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.53,1:44:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's ready
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.15,1:44:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.89,1:45:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you can rattle the gates of heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.54,1:45:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a little bit
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.04,1:45:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.58,1:45:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.43,1:45:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.66,1:45:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just wanted to meet you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.36,1:45:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in person
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.28,1:45:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.84,1:45:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from Australia
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.04,1:45:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've travelled around the world
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.92,1:45:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.78,1:45:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.30,1:45:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.60,1:45:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,extraordinarily happy to be here
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.52,1:45:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.40,1:45:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.54,1:45:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you for your work
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.96,1:45:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and for being in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.34,1:45:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.24,1:45:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to ask
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.90,1:45:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for a blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.92,1:45:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for myself
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.22,1:45:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and for my friend James
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.62,1:45:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and for everyone connected
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.66,1:45:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.96,1:45:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.04,1:46:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding it in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.76,1:46:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless the divinity within you
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.59,1:46:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and make you aware of that divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.23,1:46:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,amen
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.67,1:46:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,blessing comes from the divinity within you
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.72,1:46:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,owning it and recognizing it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.31,1:46:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.54,1:46:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.24,1:46:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not different than life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.80,1:46:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.74,1:46:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you too
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.19,1:46:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to have life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.77,1:46:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the order to be blessed
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.01,1:46:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.51,1:46:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.89,1:46:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what was it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.79,1:46:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to have life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.54,1:46:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize that
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.80,1:46:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one is
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.93,1:46:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.33,1:46:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,experience
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.74,1:46:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the expression of divinity within oneself as
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.48,1:46:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as life
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.48,1:46:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that life and divinity are one and the same
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.54,1:46:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,life is indestructible
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.47,1:46:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.29,1:46:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the one thing you're gonna have
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.99,1:46:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is life
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.05,1:46:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,not gonna have the body
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.29,1:46:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can have life
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.92,1:47:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.92,1:47:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with life goes awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.32,1:47:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.04,1:47:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that's divine gift
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.62,1:47:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you want me to do
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.91,1:47:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where did I get this
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.13,1:47:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,yes sir
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.07,1:47:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,yes indeed
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.64,1:47:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,look to Ron and here's this lady looking at me right there
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.08,1:47:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.45,1:47:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,she had a body somewhere
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.65,1:47:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't it be just a spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.85,1:47:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of body
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.93,1:47:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way from Australia
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.46,1:47:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,wow
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.36,1:47:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came from down the street
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.66,1:47:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also wanted to say thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.86,1:47:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.38,1:47:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.54,1:48:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much Susan
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.64,1:48:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had a picture with you
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.96,1:48:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can I have one too
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.52,1:48:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.08,1:48:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.38,1:48:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,well they took off the supersonic jets
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.50,1:48:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which I've been mad about ever since
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.16,1:48:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just cause a plane lost a tire on the runway
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.62,1:48:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they gotta take off all the jets
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.34,1:48:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not fair
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.00,1:48:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,oh you better
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.83,1:48:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.49,1:48:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that's it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.16,1:48:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we blew it out somehow
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.44,1:48:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't we
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.14,1:48:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
